# discord.js — official sources first

Before implementing or changing Discord bot behavior, read and follow the project skill:

- `.cursor/skills/discord-js-docs/SKILL.md`
- Load `.cursor/skills/discord-js-docs/references/official-sources.md` when you need canonical URLs or search patterns.

Match `discord.js` and `@discordjs/*` versions from this repo’s `package.json`. Prefer https://discord.js.org/ (API), https://discordjs.guide/ (patterns), https://github.com/discordjs (source and related packages), and https://discord.com/developers/docs/ for platform rules. Use targeted `site:discord.js.org` / `site:discordjs.guide` / `site:github.com/discordjs` searches before generic web search; verify any non-official answer against current docs.
